<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">The personal data we need</h2>
<div>
    <p>The personal data we collect includes:</p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>names</li>
        <li>addresses</li>
        <li>contact details</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<p>
    We are allowed to process your data because we have official authority as the
    environmental regulators for the WEEE regulations. The lawful basis for processing your
    personal data is to perform a task in the public interest that is set out in law.
</p>

<p>
    If you do not give us the information requested, you may be in breach of your conditions of
    approval which could lead to your approval being withdrawn and / or prosecution.
</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Your responsibility</h2>
<p>
    If you have included personal data about any other individuals in your submissions to WEEE
    Online, you must inform them. You must provide them with a copy of this privacy policy so
    that they are aware of how their personal data will be used.
</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What we do with your personal data</h2>
<p>We use the personal data to regulate you in accordance with the WEEE regulations.</p>
<p>We do not use your data to make an automated decision or for automated profiling.</p>
<p>
    We will share your personal data with:
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>our IT suppliers who host and provide the WEEE Online service</li>
        <li>Shared Services Connected Ltd (SSCL) who process your personal information to send invoices on our behalf</li>
    </ul>
</p>
<p>
    We put the following personal data on a public register:
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>names (Producer Compliance Scheme, Producer, Approved Authorised Treatment Facility and Approved Exporter public registers)</li>
        <li>addresses (Producer Compliance Scheme, Producer, Approved Authorised Treatment Facility and Approved Exporter public registers)</li>
        <li>contact details (Producer Compliance Scheme public register)</li>
    </ul>
</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">How long we keep your personal data</h2>
<p>
    We will keep your personal data for 7 years after the end of a compliance year in line with
    our standard information retention policy.
</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Where your personal data is processed and stored</h2>
<p>
    We store and process your personal data on servers in the UK. We will not transfer your
    personal data outside the European Economic Area.
</p>

